{"tid":1612588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"謝振中：批評警方聲明不提警員被暴徒襲擊　令人難理解","createTime":"2019-10-02T09:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T05:21:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b7f7fe5e4ef3deaf7cde4a1bca7ffea790909d54","tid":1612588,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1483875_1_L_20191002172635.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1483875_1_L_20191002172635.jpg&h=9d431d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科總警司謝振中表示，荃灣開槍事件後，包括教育界及醫療界的不同組織急不及待發表聲明，指警察開槍不必要，及形容警員「行刑式」開槍。謝振中質疑，沒有受槍械訓練的人士，基於甚麼理據和知識，判斷警方做錯。<br />\n<br />\n謝振中指，批評警方的聲明中，隻字不提警員被暴徒襲擊，令人難以理解，指當時有暴徒追打警員，但有關團體被情緒蓋過理智，做法只會加深誤解，損人不利己及不負責任。謝振中表示，別有用心人士應該停止抹黑警隊，暴力傷害各方，亦不應浪漫化暴徒行為，否則會令香港萬劫不復，令年輕人抱憾終生。<br />\n<br />\n謝振中表示，警方對有人受傷感到痛心，但施襲者毫不留情以鐵枝、士巴拿及削尖行山杖襲警，質疑施襲者當時有沒有顧及警員，又反問批評者是否將警員和施襲者的生命劃一看待。謝振中說，如果警員連自己生命都不能捍衛，如何保護市民生命安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483875-20191002.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483875-20191002.htm&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmhY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=e549136a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483875-20191002.htm&h=3e57f342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483875-20191002.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cd7bd609738bd505787429611e518dad33b78e0c","tid":1612588,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:50:52.000Z","msg":"收皮la<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgm